---

This software uses the following third-party libraries:

- `python-garminconnect` (https://github.com/cyberjunky/python-garminconnect)
  Provides the underlying Garmin Connect client. Used under its MIT license.

- `mcp` (https://github.com/modelcontextprotocol/python-sdk)
  Official Anthropic Python SDK for the Model Context Protocol.

- `python-dotenv` (https://github.com/theskumar/python-dotenv)
  Loads environment variables from .env files.

This is an unofficial integration. It is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or
sponsored by Garmin Ltd. Garmin Connect's API is not publicly documented; the
underlying `python-garminconnect` library uses reverse-engineered endpoints
that may break without notice if Garmin changes their backend.
